Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://forums.g4tv.com/i/authorsicons/thing.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: FFX-2</span><hr size=1> How does it compare to FFX, in how linear it is?<br>
<br>
My main gripe with FX was that you had one path you could follow, and that was it. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.abovetopsecret.com/forum/uploads/ats3063_FFXIroksig2.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
